---
const accordions = [
  {
    title: "Shipping",
    icon: "truck",
    content:
"For all cities of Morocco"
  },
  {
    title: "Care instructions",
    icon: "care",
    content:
  `Care instructions for jewelry:

1. Regular cleaning: Clean your jewelry regularly using a soft, dry cloth to remove dirt and tarnish.

2. Avoid chemicals: Avoid contact with chemicals like perfumes, cosmetics, and cleaning agents, as they can damage or discolor your jewelry.

3. Handle with care: Store your jewelry separately to prevent scratches or tangling with other pieces. Use lined jewelry boxes with soft fabric.

4. Avoid during strenuous activities: Do not wear precious jewelry during sports or strenuous daily activities to avoid scratches or breakage.

5. Avoid water exposure: Before swimming or using water, it's best to remove your precious jewelry to prevent corrosion or water damage.

6. Regular maintenance: Periodically check your jewelry for safety, ensure secure clasps, zircon, and stones. Some jewelry may require repairs for broken parts or replacement of lost stones.

7. Avoid extreme heat: Keep your jewelry away from intense heat sources, such as direct sunlight or heating devices, to prevent expansion, contraction, and damage.

Following these instructions will help maintain the beauty and shine of your jewelry and keep it in good condition for a longer time.`
  },
];
---

<div class="grid">
  {
    accordions.map((accordion, index) => (
      <details
        class:list={[
          "group",
          "border-t",
          { "border-b": index === accordions.length - 1 },
        ]}
      >
        <summary class="flex cursor-pointer items-center justify-between py-3 px-1 font-bold text-zinc-700">
          <div class="flex items-center gap-2">
            {accordion.icon === "truck" && (
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-5 w-5"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M8.25 18.75a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h6m-9 0H3.375a1.125 1.125 0 01-1.125-1.125V14.25m17.25 4.5a1.5 1.5 0 01-3 0m3 0a1.5 1.5 0 00-3 0m3 0h1.125c.621 0 1.129-.504 1.09-1.124a17.902 17.902 0 00-3.213-9.193 2.056 2.056 0 00-1.58-.86H14.25M16.5 18.75h-2.25m0-11.177v-.958c0-.568-.422-1.048-.987-1.106a48.554 48.554 0 00-10.026 0 1.106 1.106 0 00-.987 1.106v7.635m12-6.677v6.677m0 4.5v-4.5m0 0h-12"
                />
              </svg>
            )}
            {accordion.icon === "care" && (
              <svg
                xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
                fill="none"
                viewBox="0 0 24 24"
                stroke-width="1.5"
                stroke="currentColor"
                class="h-5 w-5"
              >
                <path
                  stroke-linecap="round"
                  stroke-linejoin="round"
                  d="M9 12.75L11.25 15 15 9.75M21 12c0 1.268-.63 2.39-1.593 3.068a3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043 3.296 3.745 3.745 0 01-3.296 1.043A3.745 3.745 0 0112 21c-1.268 0-2.39-.63-3.068-1.593a3.746 3.746 0 01-3.296-1.043 3.745 3.745 0 01-1.043-3.296A3.745 3.745 0 013 12c0-1.268.63-2.39 1.593-3.068a3.745 3.745 0 011.043-3.296 3.746 3.746 0 013.296-1.043A3.746 3.746 0 0112 3c1.268 0 2.39.63 3.068 1.593a3.746 3.746 0 013.296 1.043 3.746 3.746 0 011.043 3.296A3.745 3.745 0 0121 12z"
                />
              </svg>
            )}
            {accordion.title}
          </div>
          <span class="transition group-open:rotate-180">
            <svg
              xmlns="http://www.w3.org/2000/svg"
              fill="none"
              viewBox="0 0 24 24"
              stroke-width="1.5"
              stroke="currentColor"
              class="h-4 w-4"
            >
              <path
                stroke-linecap="round"
                stroke-linejoin="round"
                d="M19.5 8.25l-7.5 7.5-7.5-7.5"
              />
            </svg>
          </span>
        </summary>
        <div class="p-4 text-sm text-zinc-600">{accordion.content}</div>
      </details>
    ))
  }
</div>
